      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "gazebosim/gz-common",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "An audio-visual library supports processing audio and video files, a graphics library can load a variety 3D mesh file formats into a generic in-memory representation, and the core library of Gazebo Common contains functionality that spans Base64 encoding/decoding to thread pools."
